title: Win32DiskcoderPetyaA
extract: W32/Petya.EOB!tr is a generic detection for a type of ransomware that encrypts files on the victim's computer. Since this is a generic detection, files that are detected as W32/Petya.EOB!tr may have varying behavior.Jun 27, 2017
